test_list_of_single_number:
assert [] == [[32]]
  Right contains one more item: [32]
  Full diff:
  - [[32]]
  + []
test_list_of_several_same_number:
assert [] == [[32], [32], ...], [32], [32]]
  Right contains 6 more items, first extra item: [32]
  Full diff:
  - [[32], [32], [32], [32], [32], [32]]
  + []
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 1024 == 32
 +  where 1024 = <built-in function prod>([1, 2, 4, 8, 16])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
